text.tspan: I never bothered to get his real name and when I asked
him for it just now, he refused to give it to me, so we’ll
just call him the Vampire. This guy is a perfect example
of the “goth” subculture, which makes sense,
considering the fact that he’s a vampire. The Vampire
showed up at this mansion about nine years ago, and
made himself right at home. Most everybody who lives
here just randomly appeared at the doorstep one day,
actually. He loves to vanish randomly into a puff of
smoke, which can be hell on everybody’s lungs
sometimes. He also says he can turn into a bat at will,
but I personally haven’t seen him do it. Overall, he’s
weird. Approach with caution because his mood swings
are dramatic. It's like he's cursed with permanently
being a teenage child, which he is. He was bitten at age
16. This guy has lived through most of modern history,
but didn't care enough to pay attention. How crazy is
that?
Vampire
Edgy little mf
Species: Vampire
Alignment: Neutral
It's dark because if I put the
flash on, he'd turn to dust
